description: When Skiff gets a crack in his hull, Thomas needs to move him overland to Harwick for repairs, but Skiff's land-sickness makes that challenging.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Tragic Magic
description: After Richard puts on an amateur magic show, Dr. Fox becomes obsessed with figuring out how his science-defying tricks are done. But as she sets about using all of her genius intellect finding experimental ways to pull off the little pup's party tricks, will she accidentally ruin the wonder of magic?

title: Oscar and the Monsters Chapter 3: Witches' Brew
description: Mortimer and the monsters must figure out how to send Oscar back to his own time, but the only person that can help is the foe of monsters everywhere: a witch. Will they all be able to work together to get Oscar back to Hedgehog?

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Prisoner #775 Is Missing
description: When old George enters Area 51 and makes the entire base disappear, Ben and the crew learn that a mysterious Prisoner 775 may be behind it all.

title: The Prince and the Swoony Swanstress
description: Prince Ivandoe and Bert take a lovely, but lost and confused, Swanstress under their wing. When finally, her memory returns, it turns out she is none other than the awful Princess Svandelyne, stuck-up sister to Prince Svan - Prince Ivandoe's greatest nemesis! And when Svan turns up, well, this can only end up in a Prince-Off. And does!
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Con of Rath
description: Ben is on a special mission when the Omnitrix malfunctions and turns him into an Appoplexian named Rath who wants to fight anything that breaths.

title: Late Night Talky Time
description: The moon is bored of taking the nightshift, since everyone's always asleep. So Unikitty leads the gang in putting on an over-the-top late night talk show to keep the moon occupied.

title: And Then There Were 10
description: Ben discovers the Omnitrix, and when it attaches itself to Ben's wrist, he discovers it allows him to become any one of ten alien heroes.

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: Drawing Time
description: When the tv goes out, Jessica and her friends make up their own story to entertain themselves.

title: Susie and Ramona Chapter 4: Witches in the City
description: Ramona sends Susie back to New York in search of new magical creatures.

title: The Flame Keepers' Circle
description: A fanatical group of whackos have taken to worshiping Vilgax of all people or aliens! And guess who has joined them, Julie!

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: Fame
description: Ben's secret identity is revealed to the world, and an alien refugee is about to detonate a nuclear bomb.

title: Bedtime Stories
description: When Puppycorn can't fall asleep, Dr. Fox uses an invention to bring classic bedtime stories to life. But the gang's presence leads to some surprising twists in these popular tales.

title: Nia's Surprising Surprise
description: Nia is planning a big party to celebrate the anniversary of her arrival on Sodor, but she finds that her friends don't remember her anniversary and are too busy to even talk about it.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Hark the Gerald Sings
description: Oscar confronts an age-old superstition.

title: The More Things Change Part 1
description: Now on his own, Ben sets out to be a solo superhero, with new alien heroes at his disposal, but Grandpa Max has other plans. (Introducing Rook, Malware, Khyber, Nemetrix alien Crabdozer, new Ben aliens Feedback & Blox, Pakmar.)

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: The Tiger Train
description: When Yong Bao visits Sodor, a jealous Thomas sets out to prove he's the braver train and challenges Yong Bao to a series of bravery challenges, only to have his plan backfire.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Catch a Falling Star
description: Movie starlet Jennifer Nocturne springs the evil Captain Nemesis out of jail and the two escape and soon, Ben and Gwen are hot on their trail.

title: The Prince and the Tickly Torment
description: Prince Ivandoe stumbles across a secret meeting of the Royal Society for the Punishment of Peasants. Upon discovery he's about to become the victim of Prince Svan's invention - the "Tushy Tickler". Can a disguised Jezebel rescue him in time?
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Weapon XI Part 2
description: The Rooters have seemingly turned Kevin and the Amalgam kids against Ben. Can Rook and Gwen help him overcome the opposition and escape the Null Void?

title: Animal Day
description: Clarence feels the call of the wild - and decides to live a new life, free of the hustle and bustle of the modern world. Recruiting a few friends, Clarence sets out to find a new place to live his feral life, but quickly realizes he lacks some basic survival skills.

title: R & Arr
description: It's Lazy Sunday, and Unikitty and Puppycorn are having such an amazing time hanging out on the couch, they never want to move! Richard insists they have chores to do, but they're unwilling to let Lazy Sunday end. The two go to ridiculous lengths to never leave the comfort of their sofa, rowing it across the castle and like a ship and conscripting their friends to abandon their chores and join Lazy Sunday… no matter how dangerous and impossible it might become!

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: The Zone
description: Unikitty keeps losing at video games to her little brother Puppycorn, so she acquires a super-powered video game controller from Dr. Fox to help. To her surprise, it actually controls other people, and the castle goes into lockdown like a real-world video game! At first it seems fun, but will she learn that life isn't a game?

title: Waterfilter
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max's trip to Niagara Falls is cut short by the horrid Hydromanders, creatures menacing them and their fellow tourists.

title: Darkstar Rising
description: Ben and co. must uncover the truth of a mysterious new villain, Darkstar.

title: Escape from Aggregor
description: Five aliens from another galaxy attempt to escape from their mysterious captor.

title: Sir Topham Hatt's Hat
description: When Sir Topham Hatt's Hat blows away in the wind before making an important announcement, Thomas and his friends race around Sodor, trying to catch it. The Hat remains out of reach until they learn to work together.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: So Long, and Thanks for All the Smoothies
description: When Ben and Rook investigate a mysterious alien ghost ship, they discover that Argit and the Vreedle Brothers are fighting for possession of a doomsday device! (Introducing Solid Plugg.)

title: Max Out
description: Gwen's older brother, Ken, disappears and she gets Ben and Kevin to help her track him down. Their investigation leads them to find not only Ken but also another long-missing relative and a startling secret of the DNAliens. This discovery comes at a high cost as Ben is left with greater responsibilities than ever before.

title: The Prince and the Squeak of Obedience
description: Feral and her gang of cat-thieves have stolen Prince Ivandoe's map to Eagle Mountain. Cupcake, the pink-poodle survivalist offers to train Prince Ivandoe to become a Jungle Warrior. So that together they can infiltrate Feral's camp and get back whats theirs. For Feral also stole a precious item from Cupcake... one that exerts a strange hold over him - "The Squeak of Obedience!"
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Cast Aside the Truth
description: Hawkodile breaks his arm in a careless spill and lies to his friends about the accident to keep from looking bad.

title: Sea Bunnies
description: Oscar discovers an underwater portal. His return ticket? An errand for Susie.

title: Seeking a Safer Sodor
description: After a near-collision rattles their wheels, Percy and Kana enlist the help of Emily to introduce new safety measures all over Sodor. However, their anxiousness about accidents push Percy and Kana to ridiculous extremes that only makes more trouble! When Percy has another accident caused by his off-the-rails safety obsession, he refuses to leave Tidmouth Sheds. When he has to leap into action to help his friends, Percy learns that paying attention to your surroundings is the best way to not have an accident.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Prince and the Golden Father
description: When Prince Ivandoe saves the life of a Wishapillar, he is granted a wish. Unfortunately, due to a poorly timed case of hiccups, instead of wishing for the Golden "Feather" Ivandoe actually wishes for a Golden "Father". And a particularly needy one, at that!
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Valentine's Hearts
description: As the other engines prepare for a Valentine's Day party, Kana is worried: she doesn't know what to bring! Inspired by Sandy's giant metal heart surprise, Kana decides that she is going to create a sparkly big heart using her electricity! Through a series of accidents, Kana realizes that the best surprise she could bring to the party is herself!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Redbird's Bogus Beach Day
description: Redbird gets excited when he learns that Batman and Robin are taking him and Bam for a drive up the coast! But when the Joker and his van Prank show up unexpectedly and ruin Redbird's beach day plans, Bam helps him realize that even though things didn't go exactly as planned, they still had a great day!

title: The Widening Gyre
description: After a giant garbage-like creature appears drags a boat down into the ocean, Ben and the crew investigate the Pacific Garbage Vortex.

title: Follow Your Dreams
description: Apple and Onion need to find a dream to follow, so that their lives don't head nowhere.

title: The Super-Long Shortcut
description: When Gordon is unable to make an important delivery on his own, Thomas offers his help, but Gordon insists on second-guessing Thomas's every move.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Memory Amok
description: When Puppycorn witnesses Unikitty do the most embarrassing thing ever, he vows he will never forget it. Desperate, Unikitty uses Dr. Fox's memory machine to erase Puppycorn's memory of the embarrassing event. In the process, Unikitty accidentally releases all of Puppycorn's memories. Now she and the gang must scramble to capture all the scampering memories, or Puppycorn will forget his life.

title: Yeti Confetti Chapter 4: Lucy's Instrument
description: Lucy goes to Yeti school to find her instrument.

title: Dancer Danger
description: Unikingdom's throwing a kingdom-wide dance, a fun event where everyone dresses up and busts a move. Everyone's excited... except for Richard, who's terrified to let loose and feel his inner groove. Unikitty knows Rick needs to express himself but can she and the others convince him to break out of his shell with some minor robotic body enhancements?

title: Inspector #13
description: A mysterious Techadon Master visits Earth, looking for the Ultimatrix. And he turns out to be more dangerous than any Techadon ever imagined.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Chapter 18: Swellington Boots
description: When a summer storm brews, the crew cozies up in the library.

title: No Day Like Snow Day
description: When a blizzard hits the town, Master Frown tries to ruin everyone's fun by pretending to be a magical snowman! But when he gets frozen inside, Master Frown must worry less about ruining everyone's good time and instead not turning into a Frown-sicle, while he's forced to experience the joys of the holiday season!

title: The Eggman Cometh
description: When vicious dragons invade Bellwood, it's up to Ben and an all-new alien named Jury Rigg to battle the flying demons and return the peace.

title: More Than a Pretty Engine
description: After a fierce storm causes a rockslide in Crumble Canyon, mountain engine Ashima is eager to clean and clear the chaos with her new friends. However, Thomas and the others are concerned: if Ashima were to help them, the mucky mess could ruin her beautiful paint! When the friends' fussiness prevents Ashima from working with the team, she has to prove to Thomas and the others that they shouldn't judge her by her appearance.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Christmas Special
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to destroy a gift for Santa to save Christmas.

title: Last Laugh
description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

title: Chadsgiving
description: Clarence is excited for Thanksgiving Dinner with Chad's parents, but Chad is worried that their unusually laid back demeanor and bizarre customs will make him look irresponsible by association.

title: West in Pieces
description: It's the old west and Mojo the Kid has robbed the first bank ever and forced the sheriff out of town and it is up to the Steamypuff Girls to save the day at a high-noon showdown.

title: P.L.O.T. Device 2: Beyond the Bored Dome
description: Dr. Fox reprograms the P.L.O.T. Device to only generate boring events, but the gang can't help but add drama and excitement to every scenario.

title: Rotten Apple
description: Onion's Dad becomes convinced that Apple is a bad influence on his son.

title: The Later Pile
description: Hedgehog convinces Oscar to tackle an overdue errand -- but this time, Oscar's procrastination habit has spooky consequences.

title: Third Time's a Charm
description: Charmaster returns to exact her revenge on Gwendolyn once and for all.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Puddle and the King Chapter 3: All the King's Slides
description: Oscar, Hedgehog and Puddle must figure out what's wrong with the King when he orders the aliens to turn all the planet's sugar into salt.

title: Tell-A-Photo/Born to Sing (song)/Move It!
description: Tell-A-Photo: As Granny assembles her photo album, the babies gather around to reminisce about all the happy times they've spent together./Move It!: Overhearing Granny making a call to Manny the Mover, Baby Bugs and Baby Lola jump to the conclusion they're all moving away from Granny's house.

title: Thomas in Charge
description: When Gordon is given an all-day responsibility on the far side of Sodor, he recruits Thomas to be the temporary "Engine in Charge." Even though he advises Thomas about the importance of listening to his team, Thomas assigns tasks to Nia, Diesel, Percy, and Kana that do not match their strengths. With Sandy and Carly as backup, Thomas must fix his errors, use Gordon's advice, and make sure everyone's deliveries are complete before the end-of-day whistle!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Unleashed
description: Trigon shows off his collection of conquered planets, which includes Acmetropolis.

title: The Transmogrification of Eunice
description: The team discovers a strange alien girl with no memory but Sunder has been hired to capture her!

title: The Prince and the Wise Wizard of Wisdom
description: Struck down by a poisonous turnip, Prince Ivandoe & Bert must seek a cure from the Wise Wizard of Wisdom. They set off, and along the way, they are joined by an equally desperate small-faced bear, a bunny-dragon, and a truly useless fairy. Once they reach the Wise Wizard however, they discover that he is a lot less wise and a lot more "sassy" than anyone could have predicted!
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Glove Glove Me Do
description: Owen's newly found gloves make him great at everything. But this greatness comes at a high price.

title: The Ultimate Sacrifice
description: Ben is suddenly NOT Ben and it's an all-out revolt as the Aliens inside Ben's Ultimatrix demand their freedom.

title: OTTO Motive
description: Kevin and Rook run into an old enemy from the Null Void while attending an intergalactic auto show. (Re-introducing classic Ben alien, Upgrade.)

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Merry Christmas Mordecai
description: Mordecai has to get through a Christmas party with C.J. without messing everything up.

title: Jessica's Picnic
description: Jessica and Nicole set out to have a fun picnic but run into challenges when everything goes wrong.

title: Permanent Retirement
description: Grandpa, Gwen and Ben visit an old maid relative only to find that her retirement community has been overtaken by a shapeshifting aliens called Limax.

title: The Inbetween
description: Apple and Onion have promised they will be there for Falafel's birthday party. However, they find themselves in a mysterious place and don't know how to get out.

title: Jurassic Fart
description: After an all-bean breakfast the teams must cross the island in silence to avoid being eaten by raptors. That's right, this episode has dinosaurs... and lots of farting. The first team to reach the other side claims victory.

title: Appleoni
description: The wrong person is getting credit for a new dance craze.

title: Percy Disappears
description: On their way to a celebration for Thomas' 10,000th delivery, Percy tries to help Thomas with his big speech, but Thomas fails to listen. While distracted, Thomas doesn't notice when Percy falls off the track and gets lost. Percy tries unsuccessfully to find his way to familiar terrain. Thomas realizes he wasn't listening to Percy after all! He abandons his delivery ceremony to find Percy! Thomas uses what he knows about his best friend to track him down, proving how well he knows his loc-amigo.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: A Jolt from the Past
description: Alien pests from Ben's youth come back, but now they need Ben's help. (Introducing Fistrick, & new Ben alien Gravattack.)

title: It's Not Easy Being Gwen
description: You think it's easy being Gwen? Well you'll have second thoughts after you check out a typical day in the not-so-typical life of Gwen Tennyson.

title: Collect This
description: Ben finally meets the ones responsible for his intergalactic TV show, and the actor who makes Ben 10 more famous than Ben himself!

title: The Littlest Tweety/Over the Burrow (song)/In Bugs We Trust
description: The Littlest Tweety: Tweety is tired of being overlooked because of his diminutive size./In Bugs We Trust: Bugs uses the babies' money to buy different toys than he promised.

title: Chapter 19: Weather Your Weather
description: Susie mulls over her past.

title: Birds Nest
description: A storm has destroyed Jodie the Blue Jays bird nest! Good thing Blippi and FETCH are there to help. While FETCH is on egg-sitting duty, Jodie and Blippi go on a heist mission to acquire the materials needed to rebuild. It's never an impossible mission when friends work together!

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: Onion Trade
description: A boy trade between Steven and Onion escalates to epic proportions.

title: Salty's Sea Shanty
description: After Salty the Diesel Engine returns from his worldly travels, he sings a shanty to Thomas and Percy about a legendary treasure lost on the island of Sodor. The two friends are eager to see if the legend is true, but their journey comes to a snag when the rest of the Biggest Adventure Club refuses to join. The young engines instead decide to go for it on their own, and Salty, admiring their courage, joins their mission! Following the clues in the shanty, Thomas and Percy soon realize that there's all kinds of treasure in the world, especially ones shared between friends.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Prince and the Legendary Rabbit Hood
description: Mistaking Prince Ivandoe for a lowly peasant, Rabbit Hood bestows upon him precious jewelry - that she has stolen from a Prince. Prince Svan to be precise! Who is none too pleased to discover his precious items in Ivandoe's possession! Ivandoe and Bert evade capture and set off on a quest to find Rabbit Hood. They must persuade her to return Svan's treasures, thereby clearing Ivandoe's princely name.
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Broken Ducky/ Watermelon Rescue/ New Birdy
description: Sonia, Hugo and Mel have Sunday adventures with a ducky toy, working as a team, and learning to share the spotlight.

title: Trampoline
description: Mary buys a new trampoline for the family, but an accident lands her on the couch for a while. Determined to fight the boredom of being stuck indoors, she discovers her neighbor may be hiding something exciting.

title: Just You and Me
description: The full moon finds Betsy withholding her big werewolf secret from Susie, who spends the night trying to figure out what her BFF is up to.

title: The Tooth About Zombies
description: When Gwen's favorite event, the Zombie March, falls on the same day as Noah's nightmare event, dental hygienist check up day, Gwen and Noah find a way to help each other out.

title: Cave Sweet Cave
description: After the Joker floods the Batcave, the Batwheels evacuate and relocate to a nearby parking garage. As they adapt to their temporary home, they learn important lessons about family and making the most of what you have.

title: Time Heals
description: Gwen travels back in time to prevent the accident that turned Kevin into a monster from ever happening. But she ends up altering history forever.

title: Clyde Five
description: Ben's country cousin wants to be a hero, too.

title: Christmas Parties
description: The Bears have been invited to all their friends' Christmas parties. In an effort to have time to crash Nom Nom's huge star-studded bash, the Bears first try to make quick stops at all their friends' parties throughout the night.

title: The Prince and the Boasty Boar
description: In an attempt to win the hand of Princess Jezabel, Boaris Von Tusk stages a tournament to prove that he is the greatest warrior in all The Five Kingdoms. Prince Ivandoe takes part, of course, for no warrior is greater than he! But so too does a Masked Knight who not only wins but turns out to be... Jezebel herself! For Jezebel is nobody's prize!!!
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Chapter 15: Croissant Moon
description: The magical creatures work together to send Mildred on a mission so they can have a special bedtime.

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: Chapter 17: Meeting of Mounds
description: The Coven challenges The Cuties to an impromptu softball game.

title: The Real Number One
description: When Thomas' #1 is covered by paint, he sets out to prove to himself that he is still number one, but when everything starts to go wrong for him, he learns what it really means to be #1.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Pulling Your Weight
description: Apple and Onion join a gym to gain the strength of seven people.

title: Best Best Friends
description: Master Frown and Brock attend a friendship-themed competition intending to ruin it for everyone else, but soon discover their own friendship in need of repair.

title: Truth
description: An old Plumber partner of Max's resurfaces with nefarious intentions and ends up stealing the dangerous Null Void Projector.

title: The Fly
description: Apple and Onion must rid their apartment of a fly or face eviction.

title: The Joke is on Thomas
description: When Thomas and Percy's plan to surprise Diesel goes awry, the two friends still manage to cheer up Diesel... just not in the way they expected!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Ashima's Amazing Arrival
description: When Ashima is set to arrive on Sodor, Thomas and friends attempt to go the extra mile in order to make the island seem fantastic! Thomas plans an extraordinary welcome that includes a tiger, painted dock, and big dance number. But when the spectacular plan gets ruined at every turn, the friends imperfect welcome still makes Ashima's arrival extra special.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Missing Cat
description: When Chelsea accidentally lets her pet cat Crumbles out, the cat goes missing! Reluctant to ask for help, she struggles to find the cat before anyone realizes it's gone. It's up to cat whisperer Clarence to interject and find Crumbles, whether Chelsea wants his help or not!

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: No Honor Among Bros
description: Rook is under the influence of Fistrick's "bro" essence, and starts to act like a bro. Can he and Ben infiltrate an alien fight club to claim the Golden Fist? (Introducing Slix Vigma, alien promoter.)

title: Hall of Mooms
description: Hedgehog tries to get her broom back.

title: Unlock the Magic: The Beginning
description: The discovery of an ancient, lost gateway leads the Care Bears on a rescue mission in the Silver Lining, a realm of natural wonders and comical creatures in the clouds beyond the borders of Care-A-Lot. While there, new discoveries expand the mission, challenging Cheer, Grumpy, and the mission team to grow beyond their present abilities and help the denizens of the Silver Lining.

title: The Biggest Adventure Club
description: When Thomas finds a treasure map he creates "The Big Adventure Club," to seek the treasure, but when Sandy wants to join, Thomas says she's too little, so Sandy forms her own club.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Girl, You My Friend!
description: Cindy, Jabberjaw, and Squiddly compete for the title of "best friend" in Jellystone.

title: A Quiet Delivery
description: Thomas volunteers to get a sleeping Annie and Clarabel across Sodor without waking them up, only to discover that it's going to be harder than he imagined.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Company Man
description: When Clarence loses the ball during a soccer game, he ends up following it into an office building, where he's mistaken for the boss's kid and given free reign to wander around. Will he climb his way to the top of the corporate ladder or end up on the chopping block?

title: Malgax Attacks
description: Ben finally manages to rid himself of Skurd... just when he needs the Slime-Biot most.

title: Oscar and the Monsters Chapter 1: Unaccompanied Oscar
description: When Oscar isn't invited to Alexa's birthday party, Mortimer tries to make him feel better by telling him about a similar time in his life. Ever the glowworm, Oscar sneaks back in time to help a young Mortimer overcome the sad experience.

title: The Emily Ghost Institute for Manners and Magical Etiquette
description: Oscar and Hedgehog go to a magical etiquette class.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Hide N' Seek
description: Unikitty is proud to be the reigning champ of Hide N' Seek Day. But when Unikitty finds everyone in the kingdom except for Richard, she hunts him down at all costs. Will Richard continue to elude the Princess at her favorite game, and if so, how?!

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Elements Part 1: Skyhooks
description: Upon returning to Ooo, Finn and Jake discover that there have been some radical changes in their absence.

title: Susie and Ramona Chapter 1: Susie's Ark
description: When Susie learns magic is beginning to disappear from New York, she tries to lead all the magical creatures to safety.

title: Ragtag
description: When the kingdom runs out of inspiration, Unikitty takes it on herself to re-inspire the citizens with a riveting game of kickball where she and the gang form a ragtag team of underdogs, who are supposed to win a miraculous unexpected victory against Master Frown, Brock & The Doom Lords. But when the Doom Lords end up stinking at kickball, and the people are uninspired by the good guys' easy victory, Unikitty switches things up and joins the real ragtag team, The Doom Lords, to help lead them to a victory that finally inspires the kingdom.

title: Ben 10,000 Returns
description: Eon is back and it's up to an older and wiser Ben from the future to help the crew defeat him using the Hands of Armageddon to win the battle.

title: The Filth
description: Ben is tasked with cleaning the Rust Bucket. But when he is tricked into letting the villainous and vile Fly Guys steal it, he must chase them down before they create an unstoppable maggot monster with sights firmly set on destroying Las Vegas.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Elements Part 2: Bespoken For
description: Ice King weaves a tale filled with drama, romance, and men's fashion.

title: Ben 10 Returns Part 1
description: Ben Tennyson is a normal teenager who has put away his toys including the Omnitrix that gave him his powers. Ben's life take a turn when he is attacked by an alien and discovers Grandpa Max is missing. To find his grandpa, Ben teams up with his cousin, Gwen, his grandpa's partner, Magister, and even his former nemesis, Kevin 11. When they discover the Forever Knights (a secret organization that deals in illegal alien technology) and DNAliens (the Highbreeds henchmen) are trading dangerous weapons, Ben decides to once again put on the Omnitrix and quickly learns he can now transform into ten new aliens.

title: Chair
description: Unikitty finds an old, beatup recliner on the curb, but sees its inner beauty and brings it home to introduce to the gang! In a series of absurd and fun vignettes, we discover how a dirty, inanimate chair comes into each of their lives and changes them for the better. We soon learn that dear, sweet Chair was too good for this world.

title: Asteroid Blues
description: An asteroid is headed right for the kingdom, so Dr Fox leads the gang on a mission to save the kingdom by flying a rocket to the asteroid's surface and blowing it to bits with a huge bomb. But when they get there the gang finds the lonely asteroid is actually a super nice guy and don't want to blow him up.

title: Pepper and the Fog
description: After the island gets covered in fog, Pepper attempts to make it to Susie's house.

title: It Was Them
description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: If All Else Fails
description: A hibernating Highbreed officer awakens and triggers a device designed to destroy the planet. Now Ben must figure out a way to stop him.

title: Birds of a Feather
description: Ben and company help the prince of the arachna-chimps, Simian, return to power.

title: Silly Hat Catastrophe!/Zee In A Bottle
description: Lloyd is selling silly hats at the factory, but when the hat machine malfunctions it starts raining silly hats on Pretty Big City!/Zee makes a giant rocket ship in a bottle, but things take a turn when he gets stuck inside!

title: Voided
description: Ben goes into the Null Void to aid the Plumber's Helpers defeat D'Void.

title: Little Prince Puppycorn
description: Puppycorn finally realizes he's a prince, so he wants to be in charge of the kingdom for once! Despite their friends' concerns, Unikitty makes Puppycorn ruler but realizes absolute power in the hands of the pup is too much for him to handle and his ideas aren't exactly great. Can they remove him from power while keeping the kingdom from revolting?

title: Giant Woman
description: During a mission to the Sky Spire, Steven tries to convince Amethyst and Pearl to fuse together and become a giant woman.

title: Rocket's Fall
description: Thomas learns that the rocket he helped deliver is finally falling back to Earth, into the ocean outside Sodor. Bulstrode, Carly, and their team of retrieval experts are on the job to fish the rocket out of the water, and Thomas wants to help! However, Thomas is so interested in seeing the rocket again that he's too distracted to hear instructions. After a series of mishaps, Thomas learns how to genuinely pay attention, but the rocket is floating towards the drawbridge. Thomas will need to figure out how to help in the best way he knows how before the rocket is lost forever.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Secret Santa
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the crew all have the same popular and hard-to-find gift in mine for their Secret Santa, their nice Christmas shopping trip to the mall turns into a crazy competition.

title: For a Few Brains More
description: Ben, Rook and Max must stop Ultimate Albedo from absorbing Azmuth's intelligence and taking over the galaxy.

title: Christmas in Space
description: The guys celebrate their first Christmas in space by opening presents, eating peppermint bark and telling Christmas stories. Benson wants the stories to be more Christmas-y but the guys keep adding scary elements, which only infuriate their boss.

title: Betsy and Ghost Chapter 3: There's A Racket In My Hope Chest
description: The witches search for Betsy - who doesn't want to be found. Can she learn to love being a witch as much as she loves being a ghost?

title: River of Gold
description: Apple and Onion find a mysterious book but they better read it fast before it disappears forever.

title: Duped
description: Under pressure from his newfound fame, Ben comes up with a plan to be at more than one place at a time.

title: Perplexahedron
description: Ben, Kevin and Gwen race Aggregor through a mysterious artificial planetoid designed to destroy anyone who enters.

title: Susie and Ramona Chapter 2: Ghost Baby Jabberwock
description: Susie, Ramona, and Barb team up in frozen time to see what's threatening magic.

title: Glow Worm
description: While Hedgehog is off "werewolfing," a deflated Oscar has a therapy session with Shark that helps him realize the magic within him.

title: The Purge
description: The Forever Knights factions have been united into one and an all-out war against the aliens on Earth erupts.

title: Bam's Upgrade
description: Feeling neglected after being passed over on missions, Bam asks MOE to install experimental upgrades to curry Batman's favor. But, when Bam's new powers are stronger than he can control, Batman - and the mission - are suddenly in danger!

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Sandy's Sandy Shipment
description: When Sandy learns about a massive shipment of sand that needs to be delivered, she is determined to help despite her size.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Sameroo
description: Gordon has a day-long assignment for Thomas and the Troublesome Trucks -- they have to transport delivery after delivery to Vicarstown! The Troublesome Trucks are less than enthused -- this "sameroo" job will bore them out of their bolts! The Number One Engine is determined to make the day "amazeroo" for them and does his best to turn their repeated route into a new adventure! After their game of "Switcheroo" gets them lost, Thomas and the Troublesome Trucks learn that routine is not necessarily a bad thing -- in fact, it can be very helpful!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Tears Of A Clone
description: Buster finds a cloning machine at Wile E. Coyote's yard sale that he uses to make another Buster and Babs and Sweetie snag a time machine that they use to open a vintage clothing store.

title: Accidents Happen Play Time
description: Ella, Rishi and Izzy are playing in the playground but Ella falls off the swing, Rishi crashes his scooter and Ben flies off the end of the slide. Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Fortunately their parents and grandparents are there to pick them up, dust them off and send them on their way again.

title: Penguins
description: Blippi wonders can penguins fly?

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: The Babies Chapter 2: Teacup Giant
description: Susie sends Alexa to the Fjords to train as a giant, but her small size causes her to lag behind. Will Alexa be able to fake it until she makes it - or are these boots too enormous to fill?

title: Frankenhooky
description: Yogi and Boo Boo play hooky from work at an old, abandoned fun park where some meddling kids mistake them for monsters.

title: Double Daddies Day/The Pickle Fixer
description: Apple double-duty organizes Father's Day for her two Dads. Will she crush it or face a Double Daddies Day Disaster? On Dad's first day as a stay-at-home parent, Stellar plays teacher to show him parenting is a breeze!

title: Too Many Unikittys
description: Unikitty comes to the conclusion that everyone would be a lot happier if they would just think the way she does, and with Dr. Fox's help, maybe they can! Unikitty copies her brainwaves into all her friends and turns them Unikitty-fied, so everyone can always be positive! But soon Unikitty quickly realizes there can be too much of a good Princess!

title: Tub on the Run
description: While Hedgehog and Max scour the island in search of a missing tub, everyone is dying to know: are things weird between them?

title: Ken 10
description: We're back in the future with Ben 10K, and this time he has a son, Ken. On Ken's tenth birthday, Ben gives him his very own Omnitrix. Ben must come to learn to trust Ken with the power of the Omnitrix. Along the way, Ken befriends a kid named Devlin. Devlin turns out to be Kevin 11's son and was merely using Ken so he could break his dad out of the Null Void. Ben 10K and Ken then team up to take down Kevin 11. As for Devlin, he comes to realize his dad is a jerk, and realizes the error of his ways. He's able to redeem himself, proving he's a good kid and joining forces with "Team Tennyson."

title: A New Dawn
description: The Time War brings Ben, Rook, and George Washington together to battle an alien conqueror.

title: Officer Moody
description: Pieces of Mr. Reese's past are revealed when his old partner on the police force, Officer Moody, visits Aberdale Elementary.

title: Fruit Caboose/ Bin Bug/ Bug Hugs
description: The bugs learn about sharing, Lu hogs the funnest role in a game, and Barnaby learns about sharing hugs.

title: The Enemy of My Frenemy
description: Gwen hopes to rescue Charmcaster. When she asks Hex to join her, he refuses saying he won't join a suicide mission.

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: The Final Countdown
description: Rook and his little Plumbers must defend the Base from a mysterious lockdown.

title: Thomas' Day Off
description: When all the trains but Thomas get deliveries, he's left to spend the day alone. With the help of an old boxcar and a battered beachball... an adventure unfolds.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Riding the Storm Out
description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

title: Mystery Boxcars
description: Kana is upset when she keeps running out of power, but a mystery scavenger hunt is just the thing to cheer her up.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Not So Easy-Greasy
description: Nia is nervous about working with Tess, the fastest -- and bossiest -- crane on Sodor! When Nia's plan for a safe and speedy delivery goes awry and causes Tess' wheels to clog with sand, they recruit handy Sandy to solve their problem. Luckily, Sandy has a new invention to get Tess up and going again: a tanker full of her Super-Slick Easy-Greasy Crane Grease! However, chaos continues to ensue when Nia gets stuck in the mud and the runaway grease spills all over Sodor! In the midst of the madness, Nia learns how to fix her original plan and save Sodor from slipping and sliding!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Etiquette Clarence
description: Clarence submits a short story into a creative writing contest, and he's overjoyed when he learns he's accepted as a finalist! But when Jeff finds out Clarence has to attend a formal dinner, he fixates on transforming the messy Clarence into a proper gentleman.

title: Susie and her Sister Chapter 2: Hot Corn Girls
description: On her 15th birthday, Susie must prepare for her Gibbous Rite Ceremony. Will Mildred be able to keep her chaotic magic in check for just one day so Susie can become the full witch woman of her dreams?

title: Mini Golf Madness
description: Buttercup takes her game winning mini golf ball, in spite of ominous warnings of dire consequences.

title: Ben 4 Good Buddy
description: Out on a desert highway, a group of modern day highway pirates hijack the Rustbucket, trick it out and use it in a daring robbery. And while Ben and Gwen are at first glad to get rid of that "bucket of bolts", they come to realize the Rustbucket is "a part of the family." In the end our trio heroes get Max's beloved "ride" back and bring down these pirates once and for all.

title: Max's Monster
description: Grandpa Max's old Plumber partner, Phil, seeks Max's help to tame the monster within. (Introducing new Ben alien, Buzzshock; Re-introducing old Ben alien, Benvicktor.)

title: Dog King Clarence
description: When Clarence's neighbor Gale recruits him to dog sit for her, he knows it will be a breeze, being the self-proclaimed "Dog King," Clarence knows all there is to know about pups. Nevertheless, Gale's dog proves to be a little more challenging than he expects!

title: Positive Attitude Theory
description: Apple and Onion spend a day in Falafel's shoes and use their positive attitude to prove he shouldn't be so grumpy.

title: In Charm's Way
description: Kevin is charmed by a beautiful girl and finds himself under her spell (literally) as Charmcaster has returned and is forcing Kevin to do her biding.

title: The Prince and the Feather Fluffer-Upper
description: Prince Ivandoe and Bert reluctantly agree to bring Princess Syllabob of the Underwater Kingdom an all-powerful Trident for her Sweet Sixteenth birthday. However, it is currently in the possession of Ivandoe's great nemesis - Prince Svan - who has found another, less dignified, use for it. Ivandoe and Bert must risk all, entering the Swan Palace and avoiding the appalling Royal Family, in order to fulfill their promise to King Axalotyl, King of the Deep.
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Winter Creeklympics
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP try their luck at winning Gold in their first ever, Winter Creeklympics!

title: The Paint Problem
description: Thomas needs repainting and must be patient as he dries, even though he feels like he's missing out.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: All Mechas on Deck/Where There's A Wheel, There's A Way
description: Lloyd's testing a wind-up powered go-cart, but a problem arises when it keeps running out of energy./Sif's coming in for a landing at the rocket launch site - until her rocket is pushed off course by a satellite!

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: A Very Percy Valentine's Day
description: It's Valentine's Day and no one on Sodor is happier than Percy -- he gets to deliver everyone's gifts to their friends throughout the island! Unfortunately, his energetic eagerness turns to panic when an accident on the rails causes everyone's presents to fall in the mud! With Thomas' help, Percy discovers a way to still deliver the feelings behind everyone's presents -- by using the gift of song!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Breaking the Ice
description: While searching a once unreachable part of the Creek, Craig gets stranded with his longtime rival, Wildernessa!

title: Vengeance of Vilgax Part 1
description: Armed with the power of 10 Alien Champions, Vilgax sets his sites on Earth. And the only hero standing in his way Is Ben Tennyson.

title: An American Benwolf in London
description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

title: Grounded
description: Ben and Gwen manage to get grounded, leaving Kevin alone to fight the DNAliens.

title: The Prince and the Kissy Curse
description: An arrogant little frogman needs the help of Prince Ivandoe to lift his curse and become the big, beautiful bullfrog he once was. Due to a technical error, Prince Ivandoe's arms have been magically replaced by slimy froggy ones. So he has no choice but to help lift the curse in order to restore his princely arms. The Frogman's hopeless attempts to find a True Love's kiss end in failure. So Ivandoe and Bert convince him that his only hope is to earn the forgiveness of The Batwitch - his ex-girlfriend - who was responsible for cursing him in the first place.
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: I Lovey You
description: Barney's magic creates a nighttime adventure in the park, but David is scared of the dark. Barney becomes a giant glowing action figure to help David calm down so he can stay and play with his friends.

title: Fast Friends
description: While Kana and Thomas deliver aquarium materials for the Vicarstown Fish Day, it's up to steady Percy and Nia to deliver the fish themselves. However, Nia gets a wobbly wheel, inciting Percy to ask Kana for a switch so she can help Nia and speed up the delivery. Once Nia is fixed, she's raring to go, but Kana unexpectedly wants to slow things down to keep the fish safe. Could this quarrel spell doom for the delivery or allow these engines to learn something they never realized about each other?
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: So Many Birthdays
description: So Many Birthdays: Steven learns that the Crystal Gems are thousands of years old and decides to make up for all the thousands of birthdays they've missed.

title: Of Predators and Prey Part 2
description: While trapped in Khyber's ship, Ben learns details about the origin of the Nemetrix, and the link between Khyber, Malware, and Dr. Psychobos! (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Tyrannopede.)

title: Tumble Dry Low
description: When Hedgehog's podcast blows up, she must decide whether to ride the wave of fame or stay true to her small but loyal fan base.

title: Crane
description: It's the first day on the job for Kareem the Crane, and he's feeling very nervous. Luckily, Blippi and FETCH are there to lend a helping hand! Working together they help Kareem to do his work. Kareem gains confidence and Blippi learns how cranes help to build a skyscraper!

title: Special Delivery
description: After being rudely interrupted by Bim Bom during her daily morning song, an angry Unikitty takes the advice of her friends and writes down her feelings into a letter with the intention of keeping the letter to herself, but then accidentally sends it off, complete with postage! The gang then goes on a wild chase through the Unikingdom mail delivery service to keep that rude letter from getting into the hands of Bim Bom, and ultimately hurting her feelings. Turns out, Unikitty's "rude" is everyone else's "nice" and the letter was full of compliments.

title: Arrested Development
description: Ben and Rook must stop the evil Robots from Dimension 12 while trapped in their own pre-pubescent bodies, thanks to Ben's childhood rival.  (Introducing Billy Billions.)

title: Carly's Magnificent Magnet
description: When Carly gets a new magnet to help Tess the Troublesome Crane load up a shipment of metal crates, she struggles with the new tool. Carly is frustrated that she's making mistakes during the job. Sandy and Thomas reassure Carly that she needs give herself time to be bad at it. Mistakes are part of learning something new! When Sandy ends up careening towards the water, Carly will have to put her new knowledge to the test and hope she won't make another mistake.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Not-So-Secret Mission
description: When he accidentally causes all the lamp posts in Vicarstown to fall and shatter, an embarrassed Sir Topham Hatt requests Thomas to go on a secret mission to Harwick for replacements in time for the evening concert. Even though he tries to follow orders "discreetly," Thomas ends up involving Percy, Diesel, Bruno, and other engines! As they travel to Harwick and the not-so-secret mission is shared between them, Thomas and friends discover that everyone makes mistakes -- and no one needs to be embarrassed about being embarrassed among friends.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Honeydew Hatch
description: Oscar and Hedgehog enter Frozen Time to help Ramona grow time babies, but Ramona and Susie's broken friendship causes problems.

title: The Final Battle Part 1
description: Albedo Ben has stolen the Ultimatrix from Azmuth and has used it to kidnap Gwen and Kevin. So Ben goes to face Albedo Ben and rescue his friends.

title: The Prince and the Sing-Songy Stag
description: When Prince Ivandoe valiantly sets free Brian the Bard, he discovers he is now stuck with him... until such time that Brian saves Prince Ivandoe's life in return. This would not be so awful if Brian didn't send all day singing accurate, yet deeply unflattering, songs about Prince Ivandoe's looks and abilities.
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Brawl Bot
description: Dr. Fox is proud to unveil her new ultimate combat machine and take it into an underground scientist fighting ring. But Hawkodile's jealous of Dr. Fox's fighting bot that's supposedly a better puncher than him and declares he can beat anything it can. To prove his point, he dresses up in spare robot parts and enters himself secretly in the bot battle. With Unikitty as his fighting coach, can Hawkodile survive the tourney, prove he's tougher than a machine, and avoid the scrap yard?

title: The Prince and the Nutty Wedding
description: When Prince Ivandoe triumphantly finds the One True Acorn during a rigged royal contest, he also finds himself betrothed to the psychotic Princess Sprinklejoy of the Red Squirrel Kingdom. Whilst narrowly managing to avoid a royal wedding, both Ivandoe & Bert end up in the Pit of Ow instead…which, all things considered, is actually preferable.
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: A Rusty Rescue
description: When Thomas throws away Diesel's favorite oil can thinking it's trash, he makes a promise to get it back and learns it's better not to touch things that aren't yours.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Chapter 1: The Legs
description: Susie must rely on Oscar and Hedgehog in unimaginable ways after a magic trick gone wrong.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Soufflé, Girl Hey
description: Babs and Buster are excited to get college jobs, but can they stand the heat cooking for the school chef?

title: Moonstruck
description: Grandpa Max reveals the story of how he met Verdona and how he eventually was recruited to become a Plumber.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: Reflected Glory
description: JT and Cash get in over their heads when they take credit for Ben's heroic acts.

title: The Secret of Dos Santos
description: Ben and Rook join Kai Green on a perilous alien relic hunt through South America.

title: End of an Era
description: The Time War races towards its dramatic conclusion, with the fate of the entire universe and everything in it since the very beginning of time resting in the hands of the Ben 10.

title: Nor Iron Bars a Cage
description: To settle an old score, Kevin voluntarily returns to the Null Void prison he once escaped.

title: Chapter 13: Jar Guard
description: Mildred's Friend tells a cautionary tale.

title: Universe vs. Tennyson
description: Ben gets dragged into intergalactic court by the other Celestialsapiens (Alien Xs) for recreating the universe (back in "So Long and Thanks for All the Smoothies").

title: Tortilla Towel
description: After making Oscar's tortilla towel dreams come true, he and Hedgehog find that running a business is harder than they thought.

title: Kana Recharges
description: Tired and in need of relaxation, Kana decides to take a well-deserved break between deliveries. When she tells Thomas that she wants time all by herself, Thomas is worried that he and the other engines have done something to upset her. Determined to right their assumed wrongs, Thomas and friends follow Kana around the island to convince her to play with them -- the exact opposite of what she needs! When a big storm reaches Sodor, Kana teaches her friends about the value of spending time alone and "feeling the hush."
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Delivery Effect
description: Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner.  Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. In an effort to get the food their faster the gang utilizes Dr. Fox's time machine, which causes big problems and really hurts Father Time's feelings.

title: Wishing Well
description: When Puppycorn uses a wishing well and it doesn't come true, Unikitty is shocked to discover the reason: all the wishes made over the years can't be granted because they're trapped at the bottom of the well (it's a dumb system.) She frees them to bring joy to the town… only to discover that they've gone a little bad after years trapped in a dark hole. Soon, they wish it would end!

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Diesel's Dilemma
description: When Diesel discovers that he doesn't JUST like to be known for his incredible strength, he finds an unlikely compatriot in Kenji -- who is tired of only being known for his swift speed. Diesel and Kenji decide that they are going to switch jobs for the day to show to the other engines that they're more than just their most obvious abilities. However, when both struggle in their reversed roles, Diesel and Kenji learn that it's not so bad being the strongest or the fastest... as long as you get to try new things every now and then!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Showdown Part 2
description: Ben must deal with a past failure while a deranged Malware launches his final attack on Azmuth.

title: Ghost Town
description: Vilgax visits Ghostfreak in prison and gets more than he bargained for when Ghostfreak begins possessing the citizens of Vilgaxia.

title: And Then There Were None
description: Vilgax and Eon team up to wipe out every Ben in every dimension!

title: Jeremiah
description: Oscar finds and cares for a magical root from Susie's yard.

title: Sidekicked to the Curb
description: When Bam is sent to take on Prank, Redbird is forced to hang back because The Joker's van is too dangerous! When Bam discovers that Redbird secretly tagged along, he's upset… until Redbird bails him out of a tight spot.

title: Field Trippin'
description: After a pit stop bathroom break during a school field trip, Clarence returns to the parking lot and accidentally gets on the wrong school bus - which takes him to a different school!

title: Baby Caterpillar
description: Unikitty takes in a radioactive caterpillar and raises it like a baby, unaware of the havoc it will wreak as a full-grown adult.

title: Night of the Living Nightmare
description: Albedo is desperate to get his hands on the Ultimatrix and he goes to extreme measures to get it. Once he has invaded Ben's mind, all bets are off.

title: Benwolf
description: In New Mexico, Max stops to visit an old friend, who's a Navajo Chief. Suddenly, a powerful storm comes out of nowhere. And behind bolts of purple lightning, a Navajo werewolf appears. As Ben battles the werewolf, he appears to be bitten and turns into Benwolf.

title: Good as New
description: While out on a delivery to Whiff's Recycling Plant with his beloved buddy Boxy in tow, Thomas realizes that his pal is on his last crooked axle. Inspired by Whiff's talent in turning junk into useful inventions, Thomas recruits Percy to help him on a scrap scavenger hunt so they can make Boxy as good as new! However, mending the broken boxcar proves to be harder than Thomas thought, but with guidance from Whiff and his "secret formula," Thomas and friends reduce, reuse, recycle, and rethink to transform Boxy into a rolling repurposed wonder!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Thomas Blasts Off
description: It's rocket launch day and all the trains get to help deliver the big rocket parts, but when Thomas is assigned a tiny part, he puts it off to help the others with their more exciting parts, not realizing that his "small" task was just as important.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Return to Forever
description: The Forever Knights threaten to use a sinister weapon to erase all alien DNA on Earth unless Ben and Rook can stop them.

title: Rainbow Race
description: Sadness levels have hit an all-time low in Frowntown. In an attempt to cheer up the citizens of the town, Unikitty and the gang load a rainbow into a tanker truck with the intention of releasing it over Frowntown. Now they must avoid the marauding Master Frown in his monster truck, to succeed.

title: The Forge of Creation
description: Professor Paradox holds the key to stopping Aggregor from tapping into the limitless power of Alien X.

title: Unfairgrounds
description: Unikitty and her friends have an exciting day at their favorite amusement park/carnival boardwalk but Frown and Brock are there to ruin their good times and drive everyone out! The park owner warns Unikitty that if attendance keeps dropping the pier ​will close forever! Can the friends take charge, save the park, and find out Master Frown's secret ​motives? What a roller coaster of emotions!

title: That's Not My Baby/Simian Says
description: That's Not My Baby!: The girls save a baby from a monster attacking Townsville but can't find the mother. Can these three superheroes manage to take care of one little baby?/Simian Says: When the Narrator is mysteriously bound and gagged, Mojo Jojo takes over his job, ordering the girls to steal for him all around Townsville.

title: Many Happy Returns
description: Gwen and Kevin pay Ben a surprise visit, but does Kevin's strange behavior have anything to do with an angry Tetramand princess, or her father's fleet of warships prepared to attack the Earth?

title: The Ultimate Heist
description: Albedo seeks a device that will finally change him back into his Galvan form; meanwhile, Ben is locked in Plumber HQ prison.

title: Elements Part 3: Winter Light
description: Finn, Jake, and Ice King travel to the new Ice Kingdom to confront the person responsible for turning everything topsy-turvy.

title: No Sleep Sleepover
description: It's a sleepover at the castle and Unikitty and Puppycorn want to stay up all night, believing something magical must happen if you stay up long enough.​ At first the friends are game to stay up all night, but as they fall asleep one by one, Unikitty worries they won't make it! How far will she and her bro go to stay awake, and will they discover the secret reason people are supposed to go to bed when the Sandman shows up?

title: Gwen 10
description: Gwen gets her hands on the Omnitrix and all its powers and now Ben has to take a backseat as Gwen 10 battles Vilgax for control of the device.

title: Dungeon Doug
description: On a trip into the world of Dungeon Doug, Oscar and his dad find themselves on a father-son bonding mission.

title: Tough Luck
description: Gwen's Lucky Girl powers return when she buys a magical stone at a magic convention in Las Vegas. However, Hex is after the same stone, and after his niece breaks him out of prison, the two set off to retrieve the stone.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: Something Zombozo This Way Comes
description: Ben and Rook must stop Zombozo and the Circus Freaks from turning everyone in Bellwood into zombie clowns!

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: Rook Tales
description: Rook's former teacher will preserve Revonnahgander traditions at any cost.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Trade-Off!
description: Darkstar, convinces Kevin to join him in a quest for an ancient artifact with the ability to help them both escape their current degenerate states.

title: Song of Sodor
description: When Nia suggests adding a song to spice up Sir Topham Hatt's new bench unveiling, he calls upon her to write a song for the ceremony, but Nia soon finds she may have bitten off more than she can sing.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Prince and the Playdate
description: Prince Ivandoe is a prisoner in the castle dungeon of Jezabel's mother, Grizabella - the unpredictable and slightly terrifying "Queen of Thieves". Whilst waiting for a royal random, Grizabella encourages her daughter to enjoy her "playdate" with the little prince. Prince Ivandoe is all too eager to do the same. However, when Grizabella demands that Prince Ivandoe perform as her Royal Jester - Ivandoe and Bert realise they need to escape. At once!!
originalseriesname: The Heroic Quest of the Valiant Prince Ivandoe

title: Malefactor
description: Khyber and his dog attacks Ben and Rook while they're at the "Olde Bellwood Days" festival, but does the hunter have other plans? (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Hypnotick.)

title: The Big Skunk Funk
description: Abuzz with excitement about the Sodor Flower Festival, Thomas is given the important task of transporting Sir Topham Hatt's prized roses to the event. On the way, Thomas' sweet-smelling journey takes a turn for the stinky when a skunk crosses the tracks and sprays the engine with the funkiest scent imaginable! Now, with the help of his friends, Thomas must find a way to get rid of the stench and get to the festival on time.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Oddjobs
description: Hedgehog and Oscar investigate problems at U.M.P.S. and meet the new intern, Oddjobs, who's a great friend but a terrible employee.

title: Percy's Lucky Bell
description: When Thomas borrows Percy's lucky bell for a dangerous delivery, Thomas isn't careful and loses the bell.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Bruno's Map Mishap
description: Bruno is beyond delighted -- he has received the gift of an updated map of Sodor from Sir Topham Hatt! He and Thomas can't wait to use it to navigate their busy schedule for the day. But when Kana's speedy whoosh blows Bruno's beloved map up, up, and away, Thomas and Bruno team up with Percy and Diesel to recover it! While searching the island far and wide for Bruno's prized possession, the gang discovers that there is something more important than keeping their schedules -- their friendship!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Andreas' Fault
description: The team discovers that alien con-man Argit has somehow become the leader of the Forever Knights.

title: Big Tick
description: A giant alien tick that sucks planets dry, lands on Earth with the sole purpose of destroying the planet and only a new alien hero can stop it.

title: Tasty Heist
description: Richard's prepared one of the tastiest desserts ever, but he's locked it up tight until the friends have their boring dinner. This will not stand. Unikitty organizes a heist, assembling the friends as a crack team to get in, get out, and eat that tasty snack without Richard knowing. But this heist has hiccups. Can the friends take the cake?

title: Kevin 11
description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Perfect Moment
description: When Hawkodile admits his love for Dr. Fox, Unikitty and the gang become his love gurus to help him confess his feelings for her. Unfortunately, Unikitty's grand plans for the perfect moment of love complicates everything.

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Instruments have been going missing from Apple and Onion's favourite music store and Chicken Nugget (who's in charge of security) doesn't want them hanging around and getting in the way.

title: The Visitor
description: A mysterious alien named Xylene shows up and wants to return the Omnitrix to its rightful owner, Grandpa Max!

title: Pet Pet
description: Unikitty and the gang bring home a tiny creature they name Pet Pet, but Richard won't let them keep it if they can't prove they are responsible owners. But when Pet Pet runs away, Unikitty must pretend to be Pet Pet until they can find him, or Richard will never let them have Pet Pet (or any pet) ever again! Will Unikitty survive pet training, or finally admit responsibility is a lot harder than she thought?

title: Super Alien Hero Buddy Adventures
description: Ben discovers his alien heroes have been ripped off by a lame cartoon and he is not happy. So he sets out to make things right.

title: Tourist Trap
description: While messing with the World's Largest Rubberband Ball at a tourist trap, Ben accidently releases some mischievous electrical creatures.

title: Kitchen Chaos
description: After a workplace injury, Richard is unable to do his servant work. Unikitty and the others take on the task of one simple chore, clean the kitchen. This incredibly boring task taxes our heroes as they find every way possible to not do it. Will they be able to accomplish this goal and bring Richard back?

title: Side Effects
description: Ben catches a cold and the symptoms wreak havoc on his alien heroes. To make matters even worse, he has to battle a creature made from cockroaches.

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple decides to help Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Susie and her Sister Chapter 1: Heathers
description: Susie's new little sister has a gift for magic, but it's causing problems for the community. Will Susie learn to accept that Mildred is more powerful, and will the townsfolk be able to accept the most powerful witch in the world?

title: Eggsellent Adventure
description: Thomas and Percy have a difficult delivery - getting eggs and other cake ingredients safely to Vicarstown for their bake-off.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Growing Pains
description: Puppycorn is sick of Unikitty always helping him out and doesn't want to be the "little" brother anymore, so he uses some of Dr Fox's 'grow taffy' to grow literally bigger than Unikitty. Meanwhile, a black hole is on its way to destroy the planet. But when Puppycorn takes too much and continues growing, he starts accidentally destroying the kingdom. Unikitty takes grow taffy and grows big as well to help out, but when they're both the size of planets, Puppycorn proves he can take care of himself on his own by destroying the black hole and saving the kingdom.

title: Election Day
description: Apple and Onion realize that the Mayor of their city is corrupt and they vow to put an end to that.

title: General HOGspital
description: Hamton gets into medical school but soon realizes it's not at all what he imagined. Buster desperately tries to find a way to bring his pal back to Acme Loo.

title: The Ballad of Mr. Baumann
description: The grouchy storekeeper has a big secret, and she's not of this Earth.

title: Chapter 20: It Takes Time
description: The island welcomes a new era.

title: Whiteout!
description: With the holidays just around the corner, Thomas and Percy are determined to deliver the mail to all the patrons of Sodor. There are presents! The problem is there's a massive whiteout snowstorm covering the entire island and preventing the engines from seeing where they're going. Overcoming various obstacles, Thomas and Percy learn that they can rely on their other senses as well as their familiarity with the island to find where they need to go and deliver the gifts just in time.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 Part 1
description: Ben, Max Ben and Gwen investigate a couple of daring break-ins, only to discover they were both once secret Plumber installations. What our heroes find out is that those responsible for the break-ins are working for The Forever King. He's brought together a rogue's gallery of some of Ben's most notorious enemies to eventually steal the world's most powerful energy source...located deep inside the Plumber bunker at Mount Rushmore.

title: Brock Most Wanted
description: When Master Frown starts ruining parties to earn a promotion from his bosses, the Doom Lords, Brock accidentally gets blamed for the calamity. He helps Frown ruin more parties to clear his name and prove he's not the real party pooper, but before long Brock is the most notorious criminal in the kingdom, and the Doom Lords hire him as Master Party Pooper. Desperate to get his promotion and save his friend, Master Frown recruits Unikitty to ruin one last party, Brock's Doom Lord initiation ceremony.

title: Shake, Rattle, & Bruno
description: When Bruno comes along to help Diesel get a heavy load to the Lighthouse, Bruno tries suggesting a safer route, but Diesel doesn't wait long enough to listen to him. When Diesel barrels though Crumble Canyon, Bruno must brake hard to keep them safe. The squeal causes a rock avalanche and blocks them in. Diesel learns to open his ears to collaborate with Bruno on a solution that uses both their strengths to get out.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Babies Chapter 1: Breakfast Errands
description: Frustrated that he doesn't know his magical identity, Oliver convinces Susie to tell him by means of nonviolent protest. Not wanting anyone in her house, Susie takes Oliver on a series of errands to help him figure it out.

title: Deep
description: Ben, Kevin, and Gwen journey to the center of an all-water planet in an attempt to finally of capture Aggregor.

title: The Trade
description: After accidentally trading away Chad's favorite baseball card, Clarence has to trade it back! Determined to become an expert, Clarence transforms himself into a slick salesman, before facing the ultimate deal.

title: Bring it On Beresford
description: On Plant-A-Tree Day on Sodor, Thomas and Diesel both want to deliver the most impressive pine for the holiday, but they'll have to compete by delivering all the other trees first. When Thomas wins the race and the pine is loaded onto his flatcar, he discovers that he overestimated the job and himself, resulting in the tree falling in a deep ditch! Luckily, Beresford the Crane has a plan to aid the Number One Engine! Will they be able to plant the biggest tree before the end of the holiday?
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: A Nightmare on Aberdale Street: Balance's Revenge
description: In this Halloween adventure, Clarence uses a special jack-o-lantern to enter the world of people's dreams. He discovers that something mysterious is causing his friends to have nightmares, and Clarence needs to stop it!

title: The New Nemesis
description: When Hawkodile discovers his old enemy Eagleator has a new nemesis in his life, the gang do all they can to get Hawk back on his foe's radar.

title: The Tunnel
description: After Clarence accidentally knocks Belson's new video game down a storm drain, Belson enters the large underground sewer tunnel to retrieve it. When Belson doesn't return, Clarence must decide whether or not to go in after him.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Summer Bummer
description: When the beach is taken over by the most excellent Bro Sharks, will the Girls be gnarly enough to save the day?

title: Snow Day
description: Craig and his friends desperately want a Snow Day, so they turn to the most powerful people they know... The Witches of the Creek!

title: Wash Your Hands, Scrub That Soap
description: Ella is getting muddy. Mei comes out with a plate of dumplings, but Ella's hands are dirty!

title: Girl Trouble
description: Gwen's cousin, Sunny, pays a visit but she's more than meets the eye!

title: New Direction
description: Uncle Grandpa and the best directors in the business help a kid in need of acting lessons become a star.

title: Counting Cows
description: When Thomas and Percy volunteer to deliver a herd of cows, they realize that the cows keep wandering off on their own adventures unless the two friends can both pay better attention.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
